edia.org/resource/Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Barbosu and her team had appealed to CAS that an inquiry by\\u00a0Chiles' coach Cecile Landi filed over the results in the event was done so after the one-minute deadline and that the American should not be awarded the score of 13.766 that lifted her to third place.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.34839615423192e-19, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999996968506826, \"rank\": 2.5561998288561334e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But USA Gymnastics said it provided CAS with video footage that was not available to the governing body prior to the tribunal's decision that elevated Barbosu to third.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 929, \"end\": 943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"score\": 0.9999043632159138, \"rank\": 9.564593128208415e-05, \"text\": \"USA Gymnastics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Gymnastics\"}, {\"begin\": 961, \"end\": 964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.34839615423192e-19, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}]},